short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extension to parse Adobe Experience Platform analytics requests

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you using Adobe Experience Platform Launch with the Adobe Analytics Connector in your website or web application? Are you tired of manually looking for which parameters were sent to Analytics?
This extension is perfect for you! Simply open the console and enjoy a clear visualization of the variables sent to Analytics!
In this first version I tried to display all the necessary parameters; in case you need a specific one, feel free to contact me or open an issue on GitHub :)
